Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times you come, the answer will always be the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.31,0:00:07.78,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,MP is Member of Parliament
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.29,0:00:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The MP never had relations with that prostitute!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.13,0:00:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, there is no way he would ever kill anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.09,0:00:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.39,0:00:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep pestering me, I have \N ways of keeping you quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.27,0:00:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have ways?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.81,0:00:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to charge me with slander or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.08,0:00:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, a secretary like you wouldn't do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you don't want Dr. Borzmann's \N name to come up in a case like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.99,0:00:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you threatening me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.36,0:00:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.16,0:00:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.39,0:02:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a tough nut to crack.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.81,0:02:09.48,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,163)\pos(338,323)}The Only Man Left * The Only Woman Left
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder he's a major politician's top secretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.63,0:02:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No we just need to pursue this further.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think a big shot like Borzmann would \N lay his hands on a prostitute like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.12,0:02:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The victim wasn't your ordinary prostitute...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Several figures in the financial world \N can be connected to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.98,0:02:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But only one person saw her at \N the hotel Borzmann stayed at.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.80,0:02:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that much to go on, I don't think we can \N prove anything was going on between them...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.47,0:02:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is decoding of her client list progressing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.88,0:02:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, the floppy has an enumerated \N password, so it's giving us a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.10,0:02:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me the floppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.85,0:02:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, but aren't you busy with \N other cases as well, Inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.36,0:02:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does not matter, just give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.86,0:02:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, there is something I've been meaning to ask you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.45,0:02:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.95,0:02:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When do you sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.83,0:03:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that have to do with this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is an irrational question.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.13,0:03:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When are you going to talk to him about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.30,0:03:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has never listened to us before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.97,0:03:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the sooner the better!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.43,0:03:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you are being too loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is in his room, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.31,0:03:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that is unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.42,0:03:38.80,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(238,0)}The Bundeskriminalamt (BKA) is the German Federal Police (German FBI counterpart)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lunge!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.11,0:03:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you are still poking about \N the murder of that prostitute...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and her relationship with MP Borzmann.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.81,0:03:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, a big one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.60,0:03:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are bing pressured by the higher ups from \N the Ministry of Domestic Affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.61,0:03:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then please take care of your side as usual, chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.59,0:03:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't cover up the case this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:03:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Lunge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.22,0:04:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if this investigation turns out to be a mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have led a distinguished career up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.10,0:04:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to be so aggressive on this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are thinking of doing this for justice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aggressiveness...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.74,0:04:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Justice...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.62,0:04:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A woman was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.62,0:04:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am only interested in the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.75,0:04:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lunge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.22,0:04:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Inspector Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.76,0:04:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.26,0:04:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've deciphered the password to her list of clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.98,0:04:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can convert the list to real names.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.23,0:04:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So anyway she is here again...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.07,0:04:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Eva Heinemann person...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:05:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't come back here without permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.34,0:05:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just when will Tenma be arrested?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you have been drinking heavily again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I not drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.46,0:05:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regarding Dr. Tenma's case...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I consider it solved for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says that everything is the work \N of a man named "Johan," but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this "Johan" is actually another personality inside of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though that case may seem unreasonable at first...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it can be solved rationally if you think about it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that is left is to wait for the police to \N capture him somewhere in the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.65,0:05:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean your job is finished once \N you put out an arrest warrant?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.32,0:05:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have many things I would like to ask him if we meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.92,0:05:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Dr. Tenma is a fascinating character.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, there is a pile of cases on my desk that need me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.42,0:05:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are too persistent!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.47,0:06:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I have always said many times...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.93,0:06:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the MP has an alibi for that night!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.14,0:06:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An alibi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.02,0:06:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.40,0:06:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because that was the work of a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.52,0:06:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to imply that the MP \N hired a professional?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've deciphered the murdered woman's client list.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.03,0:06:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The MP's name was included.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.49,0:06:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what if his name was on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would his motive have been to murder her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.87,0:06:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that is as far as we have gotten so far...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.71,0:06:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that wasn't evidence, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.59,0:06:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you familiar with the Scherhon Publishing Company?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That company releases books exposing scandals \N from time to time, as it helps them get by.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, the company's methods \N are rather unscrupulous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They hire indecent women...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:07:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to develop relationships with famous people,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and then have them document about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be more cautious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If felt like checkmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even that secretary was speechless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was really surprised, myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is as if he is superhuman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Superhuman, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps, he is not really human.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.95,0:07:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.20,0:07:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is checkmate if I go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.04,0:07:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!  Don't interrupt someone's game...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.83,0:07:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't waste your mind a stupid game.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:07:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The president of that publishing company...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.21,0:08:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...spit everything out after that little scare.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.09,0:08:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get the preliminary memo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.09,0:08:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is the memo about that prostitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.81,0:08:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every little detail has been documented \N about her secret affair with a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the name of that man...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...other than that it starts with the letter B.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.61,0:08:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, the Scherhon Publishing Company...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.28,0:08:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...had a contract with her to publish her life story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.16,0:08:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I almost forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.33,0:08:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever had contact with a man named Janker?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe he is an assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.63,0:08:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get the hell out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.39,0:09:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are moving out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't know I was pregnant, did you, father?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.07,0:09:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are going to your man's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.12,0:09:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't know I had a lover, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.13,0:09:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Borzmann's secretary, Mintach.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.93,0:09:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.60,0:09:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.27,0:09:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll listen to the details when I get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.08,0:09:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the commotion?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.58,0:10:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The secretary committed suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.32,0:10:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"MP Borzmann is innocent..."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.78,0:10:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the note the secretary left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.62,0:10:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lunge, Inspector Kaminsky will be taking over this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Reik Park case and the President \N Garland murder case, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.67,0:10:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have anything left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you are all I have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me, Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.89,0:11:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Eva Heinemann person is here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.27,0:11:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let her in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a good time, Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.65,0:12:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When can we see each other again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.90,0:12:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.11,0:12:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop by again after my next business trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't want you to go back to your wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.83,0:12:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'll call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.05,0:12:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might never come back again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I put a handkerchief soaked \N with my perfume in your bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.34,0:12:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an insignificant man...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.85,0:12:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were looking at me again, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.85,0:12:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you wondering why I always bring \N different men into my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.39,0:12:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.44,0:12:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wish you could be like them, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.23,0:12:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.73,0:12:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:12:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:12:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it is so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.91,0:13:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love this garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.95,0:13:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I just drift off while looking at the garden...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.12,0:13:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I feel like I can forget all the bad things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.37,0:13:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that you like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.67,0:13:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to plant a mimosa here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.96,0:13:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm going to make an arch of roses over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.30,0:13:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When summer comes, it will be very...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.47,0:13:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps a man like you can do it..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.77,0:13:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have the confidence to make me happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.73,0:13:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.36,0:13:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.65,0:13:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.95,0:13:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How is your dad's cooking today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.04,0:13:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't heard a word I have said.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why mom left for some other guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.75,0:13:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.42,0:13:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.47,0:14:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is, Coletta...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.43,0:14:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if your dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I ...I liked someone, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.31,0:14:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, nothing... it is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.98,0:14:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight's dinner isn't that good, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.02,0:14:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.48,0:14:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.  It's not bad, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.45,0:14:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to trouble you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for making a gardener like you do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.70,0:14:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.91,0:14:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All my other servants left me, complaining \N that they wanted more free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.41,0:14:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can help in any way, feel free to ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.72,0:14:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how about dinner tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.67,0:14:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.19,0:14:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:14:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not comfortable in these high class places...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.94,0:15:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to become a man worthy of me, you \N need to be confident everywhere you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.82,0:15:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like when you are working in my garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.33,0:15:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.62,0:15:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.41,0:15:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really confident about myself when I'm in the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the garden is how I imagined \N it to be, I become overjoyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.38,0:15:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happiest when I'm in the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.17,0:15:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who likes gardens can't be bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.34,0:15:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you loved that garden also...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.93,0:15:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that I'm a good person?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.06,0:15:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.23,0:15:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.56,0:15:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.69,0:15:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it is just that you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.98,0:15:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...seem very lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.86,0:15:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.53,0:15:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are lonely also, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.47,0:16:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think my daughter might be worried about me, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.85,0:16:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenzou...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.90,0:16:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenzou...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.99,0:16:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is almost Christmas, Coletta.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.58,0:16:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Santa Claus better not push himself too hard this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.54,0:16:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry about something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Christmas party with just the \N two of us is gonna be lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.26,0:16:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to push yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.26,0:16:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it might not be just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.11,0:17:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the man who ruined my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!  I was just cleaning, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.49,0:17:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Kenzou Tenma, my former fiancé.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.49,0:17:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're drinking this early again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.26,0:17:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I not drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.01,0:17:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just came back from the BKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.42,0:17:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to see an inspector named Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.71,0:17:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.46,0:17:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite being worthless, he dared to turn me away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.67,0:17:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When are they going to arrest Tenma, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.72,0:17:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The BKA?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arrest?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.68,0:17:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He killed my father and ran away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.76,0:17:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he was falsely accused, \N but don't give me that crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.64,0:17:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the daughter of the director of a big \N hospital, and had my future planned out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My three failed marriages are his fault, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.07,0:17:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"It was all Johan's doing," my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.53,0:17:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.07,0:17:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kid with my father is Johan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.45,0:17:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think a kid like that could kill my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.62,0:17:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.41,0:17:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is just a stupid excuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.25,0:18:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you show this picture to the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.29,0:18:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.04,0:18:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be crucial evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma is the one who did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.51,0:18:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is just as Inspector Lunge said!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.98,0:18:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma has multiple personalities!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.64,0:18:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you displaying his pictures like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.31,0:18:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deep down, you don't think Tenma is the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.19,0:18:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you still love Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.90,0:18:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you have watched too many soap operas!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.53,0:18:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was just the man who was most worthy of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.12,0:18:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An elite neurosurgeon who was said to be a genius...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.66,0:18:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had enough praise heaped upon him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.67,0:18:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And more than anything, this man didn't talk back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.46,0:18:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He listened to all my selfish needs!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Yes!  Yes!  Yes!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.88,0:18:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a man who said "yes" to everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.34,0:18:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This man was supposed to make me \N the happiest woman in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... can't be a substitute for him...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.35,0:19:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can make gardens for you for the rest of my life...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.90,0:19:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that will ease your heart, then I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.41,0:19:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so carried away just \N because I slept with you once!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.21,0:19:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are just something to help pass my spare time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.55,0:19:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just messing around with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.55,0:19:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so full of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.13,0:19:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.84,0:19:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.39,0:19:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a lonely woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.57,0:19:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm having a party with my daughter \N at my house on Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.57,0:19:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are welcome to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.33,0:20:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This dinner is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.83,0:20:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you make all of this yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.85,0:20:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, though I can't guarantee it will taste all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.63,0:20:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't this too much for the two of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.13,0:20:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.64,0:20:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom is coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.93,0:20:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That has to be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.06,0:20:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coletta...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.60,0:20:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom is home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.92,0:20:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cha...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.79,0:20:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charlotte...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.75,0:20:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.05,0:20:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honey, I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.76,0:20:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.80,0:21:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mimosa, my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.32,0:21:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw the roses!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.57,0:21:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at your beautiful garden now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.35,0:21:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And to hell with a hospital director's mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.27,0:21:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything should burn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.35,0:21:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.50,0:22:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you have finally decided to seriously listen \N to what I have to say, Inspector Lunge?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.67,0:22:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just happen to have some free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.89,0:22:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only man for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.77,0:22:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I stop this man's breathing...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.82,0:22:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I can't be happy!
